pk.contender.earmouse

Class ButtonGridFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • Fragment
      • pk.contender.earmouse.ButtonGridFragment

  • public class ButtonGridFragment
extends Fragment
    Fragment for setting up and handling events for a grid of Button objects that represent the possible answers of an Exercise.
    Author:
    Paul Klinkenberg

      • resetGridButtonState

        public void resetGridButtonState()
        Undo any Alpha and setClickable changes done by fadeButton(). Cancels any running animations on every Button to ensure the Alpha value isn't changed after this function..
